attributes.name: Name Your Strap - 1 icon
attributes.description: From today on it is possbile to create your own strap from AIGNER and decorate and individualize it by yourself! With the help of our online tool we make "NAME YOUR STRAP" possible. Decide between a large selection of options how your very own design of your strap should look alike. You can choose by a range of 10 colours like Pink, Ruby Red, Nude, White, Orange, Moss Green and Marine, as well as Burgundy, Taupe and Black the main colour of the strap. In an eye-catching contrast two symbols are used as decorations in the the same color selection as the letters. You can select the letters from A to Z, the number sequence from 0 to 9, as also a symbol of a heart and the AIGNER logo itself. The color of the seams on the letters and the back of the strap will be the same. The colour of the logo and the heart can both be chosen separetely in two different colours. To create an either exciting or even particularly special look, we also offer to decide where to put all the icons. So therefore...
